@model IEnumerable<CarServiceBL.Models.Technician>
@{    ViewData["Title"] = "About";
} 

<!-- Service Start -->
<div class="container-xxl py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.1s">
                <div class="d-flex py-5 px-4">
                    <i class="fa fa-certificate fa-3x text-primary flex-shrink-0"></i>
                    <div class="ps-4">
                        <h5 class="mb-3">Qualified Technicians</h5>
                        <p>A quality service provider should have certified and experienced technicians who are well-trained in diagnosing and repairing various car issues. They should be able to work on a wide range of makes and models.</p>
                       
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div> 
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.3s">
                <div class="d-flex bg-light py-5 px-4">
                    <i class="fa fa-users-cog fa-3x text-primary flex-shrink-0"></i>
                    <div class="ps-4">
                        <h5 class="mb-3">Expert Workers</h5>
                        <p>When it comes to car service, having expert workers is crucial to ensure the proper maintenance and repair of your vehicle. Expert workers, often certified automotive technicians, possess the knowledge and skills necessary to diagnose and address a wide range of car-related issues. </p>
                     
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.5s">
                <div class="d-flex py-5 px-4">
                    <i class="fa fa-tools fa-3x text-primary flex-shrink-0">4</i>
                    <div class="ps-4">
                        <h5 class="mb-3">Modern Equipment</h5>
                        <p>Modern equipment is essential in the automotive service industry to ensure efficient and effective car maintenance and repair. As technology advances, the complexity of vehicles also increases, making it crucial for service centers to have the latest tools and equipment to meet the needs of modern cars.</p>
                       
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<!-- Service End -->
